 ICOQuest.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: You guest posting article must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. Your guest posting article must be related to cryptocurrency and blockchain. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us, please contact us to discuss the pos\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Active write-for-us page with clear guidelines on submitting cryptocurrency and blockchain content.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"score\": 6.6,\n      \"domain_authority\": 22,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"low\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 9,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"low\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 5,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 8,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"medium\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"Focuses on ICOs and blockchain topics. Highly relevant domain for coinography.com that supports dofollow links, though it has moderate traffic and domain authority.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://digitalcryptobox.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"domain\": \"digitalcryptobox.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://digitalcryptobox.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write For Us Cryptocurrency, Blockchain, NFT, ICO, Crypto Tokens\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"rtunities! Write For Us Cryptocurrency Guest Post Guidelines for Cryptocurrency Guest Post Cryptocurrency Guest Post ICO Guest Posting Blockchain Guest Post write for us crypto crypto blog write for us submit crypto guest post write for us + crypto crypto guest post write for us crypto + write for us “crypto” + “write for us” write for us – crypto\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Submit a guest post or article directly through the provided instructions for Crypto, NFTs, and DeFi.\",\