8NrVc5nHKrq4ATQG-HgxeQRfejLLWxGg","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/backlink-content-posts.json","content":"\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"niche\": \"crypto discussions\",\n  \"project_url\": \"coinography.com\",\n  \"posts\": [\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptostix.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Unseen Engine of Crypto: Why Community Discussion Matters\",\n      \"content\": \"The cryptocurrency market is famously volatile, with prices soaring and plummeting on what can seem like a whim. While technical analysis and market trends are crucial, there\\'s a powerful, often underestimated force driving the industry: community. Platforms like [coinography.com](https://coinography.com) have become essential hubs for enthusiasts, developers, and investors to connect, share ideas, and collectively shape the future of digital finance. This article explores the vital role of community discussion in the crypto ecosystem, from fostering innovation and vetting new projects to providing a crucial layer of investor protection.\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"coinography.com\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/cryptostix-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Contact the site via their guest posting request form to pitch the article.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptostix.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency Guest Post Submission - CryptoStix.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: To write for us, your guest post must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. To write for us, your guest post must be related to cryptocurrency and Web3. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us on cryptocurrency and Web3, pl\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Direct guidelines and submission instructions for crypto-focused guest posts and articles.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Click the 'Contact Us for Guest Posting' link\",\n        \"Fill out the form to pitch the guest post titled 'The Unseen Engine of Crypto: Why Community Discussion Matters'\",\n        \"Mention that the article will be at least 600 words and include a link to coinography.com\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"icoquest.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Beyond the Hype: A Guide to Vetting New Blockchain Projects\",\n      \"content\": \"The ICO boom may be over, but the pace of innovation in the blockchain space hasn\\'t slowed. For investors, this presents a landscape of both immense opportunity and significant risk. How do you distinguish a groundbreaking project from a simple cash grab? This guide provides a framework for vetting new blockchain ventures, emphasizing the importance of deep-dive discussions and community sentiment analysis on platforms like [coinography.com](https://coinography.com). We\\'ll cover key areas such as team evaluation, tokenomics, community engagement, and the critical reading of whitepapers, helping you to look beyond the hype.\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"coinography.com\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/icoquest-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Use the contact form to inquire about submitting a guest post.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://icoquest.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write for Us: Cryptocurrency, Bitcoin, Blockchain Guest Posting Article Submission - ICOQuest.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: You guest posting article must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. Your guest posting article must be related to cryptocurrency and blockchain. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us, please contact us to discuss the pos\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Active write-for-us page with clear guidelines on submitting cryptocurrency and blockchain content.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Click the 'Contact Us for Guest Posting' link\",\n        \"Submit a pitch for the article 'Beyond the Hype: A Guide to Vetting New Blockchain Projects'\",\n        \"Confirm that the article will meet the 600-word count and is relevant to their audience.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"kryptomoney.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"The Regulatory Horizon: What\\'s Next for Cryptocurrency?\",\n      \"content\": \"As the cryptocurrency market matures, regulatory bodies worldwide are taking a closer look. This increased scrutiny is a double-edged sword, promising greater legitimacy and investor protection while also threatening the decentralized ethos that underpins the technology. This article will analyze the current global regulatory landscape and explore potential future developments. We\\'ll delve into the nuanced discussions happening in communities like [coinography.com](https://coinography.com) to gauge sentiment and predict the industry\\'s response to new legal frameworks. From the US to Asia, we will break down what investors and developers need to know about the coming regulatory wave.\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"coinography.com\",\n      \"image_path\": \"/tmp/backlink-run-20260609-055123/content/images/kryptomoney-com.jpg\",\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Fill out the guest post submission form on their website.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News advertisement [email&#160;protected] Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com --> Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com News Bitcoin News Blockchain News Cryptocurrency News Ethereum News Exchanges News Regulations News Price Analysis Bitcoin (BTC) Analysis Et\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Dedicated submission form and guidelines for contributors working in the cryptocurrency and blockchain field.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"posting_steps\": [\n        \"Open the submission URL\",\n        \"Complete the guest post submission form with the article details\",\n        \"Paste the article content and include the backlink to coinography.com\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"site_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n      \"site_domain\": \"cryptoslate.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"title\": \"Coinography.com Listing\",\n      \"content\": \"Name: coinography.com\\nTagline: The home of crypto discussions.\\nDescription: A platform for in-depth discussion and analysis of cryptocurrency and blockchain projects. We foster a community of enthusiasts, developers, and investors who are passionate about the future of digital finance.\\nURL: https://coinography.com\\nCategory: Community\",\n      \"backlink_url\": \"https://coinography.com\",\n      \"backlink_anchor_text\": \"coinography.com\",\n      \"image_path\": null,\n      \"submission_instructions\": \"Submit the list